    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>蠕行的癫狂混沌，孕育千万子孙的森之黑山羊，力之涡动，震颤闪耀的偏方三八面体，于黑星升起的奇妙之夜，邪神将至。</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >行动！行动！行动！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地球危机四伏，可是你必须行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到食物、药品、材料，掌握位面之上的踪迹，消灭怪物和人类叛军！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募干员吧，我们会帮助你找到合适的人选，培养他们的技能，帮你完成任务，探索整个区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会找到改造基地所需要的所有道具，以及数百种武器配件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验我们细致设计的枪械系统，按照真实枪械改造武器，沉浸在战术与火力穿插的极恶世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请小心，一旦失败，干员就会失去所有装备！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，你很幸运，在你的背后，全人类都会支持你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><strong>干员，欢迎来到撤离区。</strong></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><strong>行动目标：活下去。</strong></span></p>",
